description.narrative: The objective of the project is to assist in the implementation of the first phase of the Rural Power Development Program aimed at supporting reforms and priority investments to achieve the aforementioned objectives of the sector. Specifically, under APL1, the project would (a) test and demonstrate viable business models that maximize leveraging of public resources with private investment fordecentralized electrification; (b) support transformation of ECs through institutional and operational improvements; and (c) avoid C02 emission through wider use of renewable energy.
